[I] A RDF Query Library

[T] Rasqal is a C library that handles Resource Description
[T] Framework (RDF) query syntaxes, query construction and
[T] query execution returning result bindings. The supported
[T] query languages are SPARQL and RDQL.

[U] https://www.librdf.org/rasqal

[A] Dave Beckett <Dave.Beckett@bristol.ac.uk>
